{"tid":106330,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"(多圖)穿上嫁衣的她是很動人的 28歲朱千雪仍渴望愛情","createTime":"2017-02-03T14:51:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-12T03:14:09.000Z","uid":9573,"like":106,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2030d8abc23bb86b496e71e74b89945a9ec164cb","tid":106330,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T14:51:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.elle.com.hk/var/ellehk/storage/images/celebrity/feature/tracy-chu-work-study-love/21666863-1-chi-HK/28_img_885_590.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elle.com.hk%2Fvar%2Fellehk%2Fstorage%2Fimages%2Fcelebrity%2Ffeature%2Ftracy-chu-work-study-love%2F21666863-1-chi-HK%2F28_img_885_590.jpg&h=f8664736&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港小姐講求美貌與智慧並重，那這位2012年港姐季軍必定是這個要求的佼佼者！朱千雪BB憑著精緻的五官和爽直的性格贏得不少觀眾的心，眼大大再加上笑容甜，獲網民捧為「民選冠軍」都不無道理。熱愛讀書的她攻讀完中大企業傳播碩士，又修讀城大兩年全日制法律博士課程，實行讀書拍劇孖住上。即使生活已經很忙，28歲的千雪BB早前接受訪問表示，她仍渴望愛情：「即使有多忙，也不可能完全沒時間呢！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.elle.com.hk/var/ellehk/storage/images/celebrity/feature/tracy-chu-work-study-love/screen-shot-2016-11-25-at-1-13-11-am-img-885-590/21667099-1-chi-HK/Screen-Shot-2016-11-25-At-1-13-11-AM-img-885-590_img_885_590.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elle.com.hk%2Fvar%2Fellehk%2Fstorage%2Fimages%2Fcelebrity%2Ffeature%2Ftracy-chu-work-study-love%2Fscreen-shot-2016-11-25-at-1-13-11-am-img-885-590%2F21667099-1-chi-HK%2FScreen-Shot-2016-11-25-At-1-13-11-AM-img-885-590_img_885_590.jpg&h=07d585e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2012年成為港姐後，千雪BB完全沒有要停下來的意思，先是在中大修讀傳播學院碩士課程，2016年她又於香港城市大學攻讀全日制法律博士。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.elle.com.hk/var/ellehk/storage/images/celebrity/feature/tracy-chu-work-study-love/screen-shot-2016-11-25-at-1-12-54-am-img-885-590/21667083-1-chi-HK/Screen-Shot-2016-11-25-At-1-12-54-AM-img-885-590_img_885_590.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elle.com.hk%2Fvar%2Fellehk%2Fstorage%2Fimages%2Fcelebrity%2Ffeature%2Ftracy-chu-work-study-love%2Fscreen-shot-2016-11-25-at-1-12-54-am-img-885-590%2F21667083-1-chi-HK%2FScreen-Shot-2016-11-25-At-1-12-54-AM-img-885-590_img_885_590.jpg&h=e31b9319&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n她在訪問中表示她不認為進修是為了將來演藝圈以外的事業鋪路，只想趁自己年輕、沒包袱時裝備自己。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.elle.com.hk/var/ellehk/storage/images/celebrity/feature/tracy-chu-work-study-love/72f7da25jw1f4fxwkqwqxj20qo0xctdd/21666939-1-chi-HK/72f7da25jw1f4fxwkqwqxj20qo0xctdd_img_885_590.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elle.com.hk%2Fvar%2Fellehk%2Fstorage%2Fimages%2Fcelebrity%2Ffeature%2Ftracy-chu-work-study-love%2F72f7da25jw1f4fxwkqwqxj20qo0xctdd%2F21666939-1-chi-HK%2F72f7da25jw1f4fxwkqwqxj20qo0xctdd_img_885_590.jpg&h=f4e0c502&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n她堅持要一直進修增值自己，這份堅持令她成為演藝圈內高學歷女神代表之一。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.elle.com.hk/var/ellehk/storage/images/celebrity/feature/tracy-chu-work-study-love/72f7da25jw1fb961fm8m9j22io1vyhc9/21667035-1-chi-HK/72f7da25jw1fb961fm8m9j22io1vyhc9_img_885_590.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elle.com.hk%2Fvar%2Fellehk%2Fstorage%2Fimages%2Fcelebrity%2Ffeature%2Ftracy-chu-work-study-love%2F72f7da25jw1fb961fm8m9j22io1vyhc9%2F21667035-1-chi-HK%2F72f7da25jw1fb961fm8m9j22io1vyhc9_img_885_590.jpg&h=48bc99e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「我的人生很特別，很多時都是機會來找我，入娛樂圈、讀書都是如此。當年參選港姐後，有機會拍劇，好像很順風順水，到現在大學寄信來說取錄我，又好像有另一個機會，我這人總是順着河流飄，很多從未想過發生的機會都在我身上出現了，所以我更不想放棄任何機會。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.elle.com.hk/var/ellehk/storage/images/celebrity/feature/tracy-chu-work-study-love/72f7da25gw1fa64wx9ellj20qo141ahe/21666891-1-chi-HK/72f7da25gw1fa64wx9ellj20qo141ahe_img_885_590.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elle.com.hk%2Fvar%2Fellehk%2Fstorage%2Fimages%2Fcelebrity%2Ffeature%2Ftracy-chu-work-study-love%2F72f7da25gw1fa64wx9ellj20qo141ahe%2F21666891-1-chi-HK%2F72f7da25gw1fa64wx9ellj20qo141ahe_img_885_590.jpg&h=079a3a22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n漂亮、高學歷、有名氣，她明明應該萬千寵愛在一身，卻直言很少人追求。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1dYr9.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1dYr9.gif&h=07566223&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.elle.com.hk/var/ellehk/storage/images/celebrity/feature/tracy-chu-work-study-love/screen-shot-2017-01-28-at-21-13-01/21667163-1-chi-HK/Screen-Shot-2017-01-28-At-21-13-01_img_885_590.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elle.com.hk%2Fvar%2Fellehk%2Fstorage%2Fimages%2Fcelebrity%2Ffeature%2Ftracy-chu-work-study-love%2Fscreen-shot-2017-01-28-at-21-13-01%2F21667163-1-chi-HK%2FScreen-Shot-2017-01-28-At-21-13-01_img_885_590.jpg&h=96c9ba22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n她有已單身了六年多，男士們真的要加把勁了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.elle.com.hk/var/ellehk/storage/images/celebrity/feature/tracy-chu-work-study-love/screen-shot-2017-01-28-at-21-12-44/21667131-1-chi-HK/Screen-Shot-2017-01-28-At-21-12-44_img_885_590.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elle.com.hk%2Fvar%2Fellehk%2Fstorage%2Fimages%2Fcelebrity%2Ffeature%2Ftracy-chu-work-study-love%2Fscreen-shot-2017-01-28-at-21-12-44%2F21667131-1-chi-HK%2FScreen-Shot-2017-01-28-At-21-12-44_img_885_590.jpg&h=2482d2e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雖然外表女性化，但她坦言自己不是小鳥依人型女生。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.elle.com.hk/var/ellehk/storage/images/celebrity/feature/tracy-chu-work-study-love/72f7da25jw1fajh57ijuvj20b30ge0t4/21666971-1-chi-HK/72f7da25jw1fajh57ijuvj20b30ge0t4_img_885_590.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elle.com.hk%2Fvar%2Fellehk%2Fstorage%2Fimages%2Fcelebrity%2Ffeature%2Ftracy-chu-work-study-love%2F72f7da25jw1fajh57ijuvj20b30ge0t4%2F21666971-1-chi-HK%2F72f7da25jw1fajh57ijuvj20b30ge0t4_img_885_590.jpg&h=e75cf347&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n那有什麼擇偶條件呢？「我只在乎襯不襯我，於我而言，最重要是兩個人可以好好溝通、互相明白、互相學習，或者我可以跟一個完全不同行業的人聊得上&hellip;&hellip;拍拖不是要找一個和我一模一樣的人，否則就和自己拍拖一樣了。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.elle.com.hk/var/ellehk/storage/images/celebrity/feature/tracy-chu-work-study-love/72f7da25jw1fajh59w8wxj20aw0gedgi/21666987-1-chi-HK/72f7da25jw1fajh59w8wxj20aw0gedgi_img_885_590.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elle.com.hk%2Fvar%2Fellehk%2Fstorage%2Fimages%2Fcelebrity%2Ffeature%2Ftracy-chu-work-study-love%2F72f7da25jw1fajh59w8wxj20aw0gedgi%2F21666987-1-chi-HK%2F72f7da25jw1fajh59w8wxj20aw0gedgi_img_885_590.jpg&h=c3b1ee02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n可是面對結婚的問題，千雪BB表示：「我和結婚的距離？很遠呢！」可是看她穿起婚紗的照片，完全是一副幸福新娘的模樣，也許幸福已在不知不覺間走近她的身邊。"},{"pid":"137a7b60dbe1c626676d6bc5957a7d075d3a3973","tid":106330,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T14:51:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.elle.com.hk/var/ellehk/storage/images/celebrity/feature/tracy-chu-work-study-love/72f7da25jw1f0z0edmbu2j21ho1zkx6r/21666907-1-chi-HK/72f7da25jw1f0z0edmbu2j21ho1zkx6r_img_885_590.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elle.com.hk%2Fvar%2Fellehk%2Fstorage%2Fimages%2Fcelebrity%2Ffeature%2Ftracy-chu-work-study-love%2F72f7da25jw1f0z0edmbu2j21ho1zkx6r%2F21666907-1-chi-HK%2F72f7da25jw1f0z0edmbu2j21ho1zkx6r_img_885_590.jpg&h=81383457&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n去年情人節，千雪BB就搞鬼po出西蘭花照，不知女神什麼時候可以遇上對的人呢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.elle.com.hk/var/ellehk/storage/images/celebrity/feature/tracy-chu-work-study-love/screen-shot-2017-01-28-at-21-13-09/21667179-1-chi-HK/Screen-Shot-2017-01-28-At-21-13-09_img_885_590.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elle.com.hk%2Fvar%2Fellehk%2Fstorage%2Fimages%2Fcelebrity%2Ffeature%2Ftracy-chu-work-study-love%2Fscreen-shot-2017-01-28-at-21-13-09%2F21667179-1-chi-HK%2FScreen-Shot-2017-01-28-At-21-13-09_img_885_590.jpg&h=3fcae347&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n愛讀書的她亦較喜歡文靜型的男生，不希望對方有太多朋友或時常出去玩。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.elle.com.hk/var/ellehk/storage/images/celebrity/feature/tracy-chu-work-study-love/screen-shot-2017-01-28-at-21-05-52/21667115-1-chi-HK/Screen-Shot-2017-01-28-At-21-05-52_img_885_590.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elle.com.hk%2Fvar%2Fellehk%2Fstorage%2Fimages%2Fcelebrity%2Ffeature%2Ftracy-chu-work-study-love%2Fscreen-shot-2017-01-28-at-21-05-52%2F21667115-1-chi-HK%2FScreen-Shot-2017-01-28-At-21-05-52_img_885_590.jpg&h=25b049a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n熱愛學習的千雪BB並沒有為學業而停工，卻依然拍劇上學兩邊走，前排她就公開自己的行程，連續24小時沒有停過：「Non-stop 24 hours！ School in the morning, commercial shoot in the afternoon, drama overnight. 6AM yesterday, good morning...6AM today, good night！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.elle.com.hk/var/ellehk/storage/images/celebrity/feature/tracy-chu-work-study-love/72f7da25jw1faudd7dn7nj22io1vy7wh/21667003-1-chi-HK/72f7da25jw1faudd7dn7nj22io1vy7wh_img_885_590.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elle.com.hk%2Fvar%2Fellehk%2Fstorage%2Fimages%2Fcelebrity%2Ffeature%2Ftracy-chu-work-study-love%2F72f7da25jw1faudd7dn7nj22io1vy7wh%2F21667003-1-chi-HK%2F72f7da25jw1faudd7dn7nj22io1vy7wh_img_885_590.jpg&h=9e8b41f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n又要讀書又要拍劇，朱千雪po出「書本」照片：「讀完課本，代表要開始讀劇本了。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.elle.com.hk/var/ellehk/storage/images/celebrity/feature/tracy-chu-work-study-love/screen-shot-2017-01-28-at-21-12-53/21667147-1-chi-HK/Screen-Shot-2017-01-28-At-21-12-53_img_885_590.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elle.com.hk%2Fvar%2Fellehk%2Fstorage%2Fimages%2Fcelebrity%2Ffeature%2Ftracy-chu-work-study-love%2Fscreen-shot-2017-01-28-at-21-12-53%2F21667147-1-chi-HK%2FScreen-Shot-2017-01-28-At-21-12-53_img_885_590.jpg&h=b78cd993&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n粉絲都為她感到心痛，留言叫她要加油和多休息<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.elle.com.hk/var/ellehk/storage/images/celebrity/feature/tracy-chu-work-study-love/72f7da25jw1faw1uf1iw7j20te18gwks/21667019-1-chi-HK/72f7da25jw1faw1uf1iw7j20te18gwks_img_885_590.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elle.com.hk%2Fvar%2Fellehk%2Fstorage%2Fimages%2Fcelebrity%2Ffeature%2Ftracy-chu-work-study-love%2F72f7da25jw1faw1uf1iw7j20te18gwks%2F21667019-1-chi-HK%2F72f7da25jw1faw1uf1iw7j20te18gwks_img_885_590.jpg&h=8e7c77aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2016年她憑著《EU超時任務》一角與王浩信齊齊拿到最喜愛螢幕情侶獎。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.elle.com.hk/var/ellehk/storage/images/celebrity/feature/tracy-chu-work-study-love/72f7da25jw1fbin5vog0tj21zk1honpg/21667051-1-chi-HK/72f7da25jw1fbin5vog0tj21zk1honpg_img_885_590.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elle.com.hk%2Fvar%2Fellehk%2Fstorage%2Fimages%2Fcelebrity%2Ffeature%2Ftracy-chu-work-study-love%2F72f7da25jw1fbin5vog0tj21zk1honpg%2F21667051-1-chi-HK%2F72f7da25jw1fbin5vog0tj21zk1honpg_img_885_590.jpg&h=927cbcf9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n新劇《踩過界》拍攝花絮<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.elle.com.hk/var/ellehk/storage/images/celebrity/feature/tracy-chu-work-study-love/72f7da25jw1fbnmx8hsy5j20xc139e81/21667067-1-chi-HK/72f7da25jw1fbnmx8hsy5j20xc139e81_img_885_590.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elle.com.hk%2Fvar%2Fellehk%2Fstorage%2Fimages%2Fcelebrity%2Ffeature%2Ftracy-chu-work-study-love%2F72f7da25jw1fbnmx8hsy5j20xc139e81%2F21667067-1-chi-HK%2F72f7da25jw1fbnmx8hsy5j20xc139e81_img_885_590.jpg&h=4f861f13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當年8歲的她已經是個小美人，祝福千雪早日找到好歸宿<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ！"},{"pid":"63e4b3a2f21ab0900381f1045989460e0a585a8f","tid":106330,"uid":65587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T15:16:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4607a7ebe376a7fe35db0d51ed68e1f92b96ae7f","tid":106330,"uid":80183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T15:21:24.000Z","msg":"個口大到塞幾條撚都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29e83152bb8d7afd49a6922de95255df47ecc103","tid":106330,"uid"